Rating: 4
If you like cheesecake, chances are you like cream cheese. During warmer months, this pie is perfect as a no-bake, PLUS cream cheese flavor is not altered by baking. Many times I prefer the no-bake as it more quickly satiates the cream cheese hankering - no eggs or other ingredients to get in the way. Recipe is also very malleable. Thanks!

